              "messages": {
                "default": [
                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to handle objections by offering compromises.\nWhen a client is unsure, you can suggest a smaller step or offer helpful information.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/f3329625-7e33-4dc5-b77f-789059add89c-Objection-Handling---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "First, suggest a compromise to make the client comfortable.\nUse: 'How about we [compromise] first?'\nExample: 'How about we try a 3-month pilot first?'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/f3329625-7e33-4dc5-b77f-789059add89c-Objection-Handling---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "Next, offer to send something useful to help them decide.\nUse: 'I can send you [item] by [day] to help you decide.'\nExample: 'I can send you a comparison report by Monday to help you decide.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/f3329625-7e33-4dc5-b77f-789059add89c-Objection-Handling---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "You can also offer a flexible starting point.\nUse: 'If [option] works for you, we can start with that.'\nExample: 'If a smaller rollout works for you, we can start with that.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/f3329625-7e33-4dc5-b77f-789059add89c-Objection-Handling---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Now let's practice handling objections by offering next steps!",
                    "media": {
